Prints the value of a preference.

usage: getpreference
       [{ -? | --help }]
       [{ -d | --default} <defaultvalue>]
       [--onlyvalue]
       <name>
 -?
--help
  Show this help text
 -d
--default
  A default value if there is no value set.
--onlyvalue
  Only prints the value (if any).
<name>
  The name of the preference

